@11001 = ~Neutralize Poison

Range: 10 yards
Duration: Instant
Area of Effect: 1 creature

This ability removes all toxins from the body, both natural and magical in nature. When this ability is cast upon a poisoned individual, it immediately neutralizes any poison and restores 10 lost Hit Points. This ability will also cure any diseases that the target might be suffering from, as well as blindness and deafness.~
@11002 = ~Missile Blast

